    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到《神奈学园》，一款非常有趣和创新的横版塔防游戏！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美的动漫Q版人物：游戏中的角色设计精致可爱，每一个角色都栩栩如生，带给你视觉上的享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >舒适的UI设计：采用观感舒适的动漫插画风格，让你在游戏过程中享受美妙的视觉体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创新的战斗运营系统：独特的战斗运营系统，让你在策略与操作中找到平衡，体验前所未有的战斗乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue元素：结合Rogue元素的横版塔防玩法，每一次游戏都是全新的挑战和冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《神奈学园》中，你将指挥由动漫角色组成的队伍，在学园教室中迎战机器人AI和各种异世界敌人的入侵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含超过10组动漫角色队伍，每组队伍都拥有其独一无二的战斗风格和技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更令人期待的是，游戏将持续更新，带来更多精彩内容和角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039990/extras/684d0db441addfe4eb02a3312ee59a2f.avif?t=1728155466\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039990/extras/48254ba548c6360482897135d6108dd2.avif?t=1728155466\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039990/extras/e9785294a7d99e0346e28b024d60020e.avif?t=1728155466\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039990/extras/483d359bef92053fdc9157c56ebb57a4.avif?t=1728155466\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p>",
